  "texts": [
    "Background: The integration of large language models (LLMs) in healthcare offers immense opportunity to streamline healthcare tasks, but also carries risks such as response accuracy and bias perpetration.",
    "To address this, we conducted a red-teaming exercise to assess LLMs in healthcare and developed a dataset of clinically relevant scenarios for future teams to use.",
    "Large language models (LLMs) are a class of generative AI models capable of processing and generating human-like text at a large scale 1.",
    "However, LLMs are susceptible to inaccuracies and biases in their training data.",
    "The objective of an LLM is to iteratively predict the next most likely word or word part."
  ],
